\title{Deligne's "Hodge Theory I, II, and III"}

\import{macros}

\p{
  This is an English translation of \strong{P. Deligne}'s three papers on Hodge theory:
  \ul{
    \li{
      "Théorie de Hodge I", \em{Actes du Congrès intern. math.} \strong{1} (1970) pp. 425–430.
      [[PDF]](https://publications.ias.edu/node/359)
    }
    \li{
      "Théorie de Hodge II", \em{Pub. Math. de l'IHÉS} \strong{40} (1971) pp. 5–58.
      [[PDF]](https://publications.ias.edu/node/361)
    }
    \li{
      "Théorie de Hodge III", \em{Pub. Math. de l'IHÉS} \strong{44} (1974) pp. 5–77.
      [[PDF]](https://publications.ias.edu/node/373)
    }
  }
}

